Listen to your Emma.

41:38.763 --> 41:41.464
<i> Like an angel's dream</i>
<i> of an angel.</i>

41:41.800 --> 41:45.034
<i> Through her, I finally see</i>
<i> how to do it.</i>

41:46.304 --> 41:48.705
How to make the worm turn.

41:49.941 --> 41:50.874
Hello? Who is this?

41:50.876 --> 41:52.542
<i> # The valley of death</i>
<i> may not find you</i>

